	- upload the php file
	- append /upload/{$randomFileName}.php in the URL
	- now in the URL type the query 'q=cat%20/etc/natas_webpass/natas13'
	- Password: trbs5pCjCrkuSknBBKHhaBxq6Wm1j3LC 

